{"tid":1650044,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"大家係咪搞錯咗不分化不割蓆嘅意思？","createTime":"2019-10-12T19:55:12.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-12T20:09:20.000Z","uid":312488,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"bdb85788c285d73881cf4028c094f250d32ba914","tid":1650044,"uid":312488,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-12T19:55:12.000Z","msg":"係咪得我理解係<br />\n不分化＝大家各有各做，和勇一家。<br />\n不割蓆＝不管大家啲行動做到咩程度幾激烈完唔完美，只要係為呢場運動所做嘅都接受。<br />\n屌嗰班蛋糕撚絕對唔係分化／割蓆，因為佢地嘅行為同運動無關甚至無益。<span style=\"font-size: small;\">篤灰就真係做多咗</span><br />\n但為咗幾個蛋糕撚自己友互屌有意思咩？<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: large;\">不如推返行動post啦</span></span></strong><br />\n[url]［行動post］10月13日！18區開花！<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1649940[/url]\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1649940[/url]</a>"},{"pid":"1fcefb5ca749f43a275f3afee062b5d018d6c08b","tid":1650044,"uid":312692,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-12T19:58:05.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/MCm85ni.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FMCm85ni.jpg&h=5231a172&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong>10.13 10.14 不見不散</strong></span></span>"},{"pid":"041562cdf76d11d583bf9ed9dff3fc0f33bb07d9","tid":1650044,"uid":2689,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-12T19:59:22.000Z","msg":"唔好再就蛋糕事件開post屌啦<br />\n仲唔夠多咩<br />\n要屌要傾集中去屌<br />\n<br />\n18區啊聽日"},{"pid":"b0bacde0cbdedc88627651f3c60a35fe4cfa91a9","tid":1650044,"uid":312488,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-12T19:59:46.000Z","msg":"[行動post] 起身熱門仲要睇到呢個post！！！<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1649823\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1649823</a>"},{"pid":"11e8f80170293ef92fd23ad44f1701287b04d69b","tid":1650044,"uid":325269,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-12T20:09:20.00